snippet.title: Best VGM 1326 - Mega Turrican - Stage 5-1 (Machine World)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 60 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DLqos66n3Qo

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Sega Genesis
Mega Turrican (1994)
Stage 5-1 (Machine World)
Chris Hulsbeck
